{
  "texts": [
    "In the MooAnalytica research group of Dalhousie University, researchers adopt these AI-assisted techniques to optimize the annotation process, reducing both time and costs while maintaining high accuracy.",
    "By employing these advanced tools, they efficiently manage large datasets across various breeds and environments, illustrating that annotation is no longer a limiting factor in scaling HACI technologies.",
    "The integration of HACI in farm settings opens up new avenues for enhancing the welfare of farm animals.",
    "This innovative approach goes beyond meeting the physical needs of the animals, focusing also on enriching their emotional well-being.",
    "HACI technologies facilitate better emotional interactions between humans and animals and improve our understanding of animal behavior."
  ]
}